caption.body: Flight attendant Ruby Reykalin is seen here conversing on the telephone at United Air Lines exhibit in Vacation Lands Building at Golden Gate International Exposition, Treasure Island, San Francisco. The United exhibit was one of three aviation exhibits at the Golden Gate International Exposition. #WomenInAviation  United Air Lines c. 1940 SFO Museum Collection Gift of Kathryn McGeorge 2011.194.016
